Class Database

  • java.lang.Object
    • Database

  • public class Database
extends java.lang.Object
    This class deffines objects such as items, abilities or enemies. All objects are divided into lists. All items are defined in constructor, and shouldn't be added to database object from any other place in program, or any other class. Object of this class preferably should be generated only once (at start of program), and shouldn't be used inside player class objects(as player class objects may serve as save files in future, and including database of inside player class objects, will render saves incompatible with future versions)
